<div class="tool-panel guide-panel">
  <div class="guide-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>本地生成</strong>
      <p>使用浏览器 Web Crypto 生成随机值，适合粘贴到 .env 文件。</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong>可直接复制</strong>
      <p>生成后可复制单个变量，也可以一次复制完整的 .env 片段。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="action-row" aria-label="Credentials 操作">
  <button type="button" data-credentials-action="generate">生成</button>
  <button type="button" data-credentials-action="copy-all" disabled>复制全部</button>
  <button type="button" data-credentials-action="download" disabled>下载 .env 片段</button>
</div>

<div class="status-line" data-status data-state="ok">
  <span aria-hidden="true">●</span>
  <span>等待生成</span>
</div>

<div class="tool-panel result-panel">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <h2>Credentials</h2>
    <span>.env secrets</span>
  </div>
  <div class="credential-list" data-credential-list aria-live="polite">
    <p class="empty-state small">点击生成后会显示密钥。</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="tool-panel">
  <label class="field-label" for="credentials-output">.env 输出</label>
  <textarea id="credentials-output" readonly spellcheck="false" placeholder="生成后的 .env 片段会显示在这里"></textarea>
</div>
